note over browser:
New note is added to list
via js redraw handler
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa 

note over server:
server receives note in 
JSON format and saves it
end note

server-->browser: HTTP 201

note over browser:
browser does not
reload the page
end note

note over browser:
console logs 
{"message":"note created"}
from spa.js
end note